## Semantic Conventions (semconv/)

The semantic conventions defined in this project are inspired by and draw
concepts from the following projects:

### o11y-by-design
  URL: https://github.com/jsuereth/o11y-by-design
  The design philosophy and structure of the semantic conventions in this
  project are influenced by the observability-by-design patterns described
  in this repository.

### OpenTelemetry Semantic Conventions
  URL: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions
  License: Apache License 2.0
  The naming conventions, attribute definitions, and overall structure of
  the semconv/ directory are inspired by the OpenTelemetry Semantic
  Conventions project. OpenTelemetry is a CNCF project.

